            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Emergency info buried costs 12 minutes crisis time</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">School closure test. School A: emergency info 3 clicks deep. Avg find time: 47 seconds. School B: banner immediately. Avg find time: 8 seconds. Seconds matter in emergencies.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
